## 2. Homebrew Tap Setup

Lets macOS users install with: brew install --cask gilfoyle

Step 1: Create a PUBLIC GitHub repo named "homebrew-gilfoyle" under AadityaMishra1
        https://github.com/new

Step 2: Add file Casks/gilfoyle.rb with this content:

    cask "gilfoyle" do
      version "0.1.0"
      sha256 "REPLACE_WITH_SHA256"

      url "https://github.com/AadityaMishra1/Gilfoyle/releases/download/v#{version}/Gilfoyle-#{version}-universal.dmg"
      name "Gilfoyle"
      desc "Desktop GUI for Claude Code CLI"
      homepage "https://github.com/AadityaMishra1/Gilfoyle"

      depends_on formula: "node"

      app "Gilfoyle.app"

      zap trash: [
        "~/Library/Application Support/gilfoyle",
        "~/.gilfoyle",
      ]
    end

Step 3: After your first GitHub Release builds the DMG, get the SHA256:
    shasum -a 256 Gilfoyle-0.1.0-universal.dmg
    Paste the hash replacing REPLACE_WITH_SHA256

Step 4: Push and test:
    brew tap AadityaMishra1/gilfoyle
    brew install --cask gilfoyle

Step 5: On each new release, update version + sha256, push to tap repo.


## 3. First Release - Do This In Order

 1. Take all screenshots above
 2. Add the best ones to README.md
 3. Commit everything
 4. Tag: git tag v0.1.0 && git push origin v0.1.0
 5. Wait for CI release workflow to build DMG/EXE/AppImage
 6. Download macOS DMG from the release
 7. Run: shasum -a 256 Gilfoyle-*.dmg
 8. Create homebrew-gilfoyle repo with Casks/gilfoyle.rb + SHA256
 9. Test: brew tap AadityaMishra1/gilfoyle && brew install --cask gilfoyle
10. Share the repo


## 4. Distribution Channels

| Channel                          | Status                          | Effort  |
|----------------------------------|---------------------------------|---------|
| GitHub Releases (DMG/EXE/AppImage) | Ready - CI builds on tag push | Done    |
| Homebrew Cask                    | Needs tap repo created          | 15 min  |
| Winget (Windows)                 | Submit manifest after release   | 30 min  |
| AUR (Arch Linux)                 | Write PKGBUILD, no approval     | 20 min  |
| Official Homebrew Cask           | Needs 225+ GitHub stars first   | Later   |
| macOS code signing ($99/yr)      | Eliminates Gatekeeper warning   | Later   |
| Windows Authenticode (~$120/yr)  | Eliminates SmartScreen warning  | Later   |
